3-ne 12:
[center][font_size=26]Iralaud 12[/font_size][/center]

[i]Sises malipe oh kihong irail manaman rehn tohnpadahk ehk riemeno—E ketikihong Mehn Nihpai kan padahk me duwehte sapwellime Kapahrek en Pohn Dohlo—E mahsanih duwen Meid Pai kan—Sapwellime padahngkan siksang oh weliandi kosonned en Moseso—Re ketin mahsanih me aramas en unsek duwehte Ih oh Semehu me unsek—Karasahiong Madiu 5. Ele Sounpar 34 Mwurin Ipwidi en Krais.[/i]

1 Kedekedeo ahnsou me Sises mahsanihongehr mahsen pwukat rehn Nihpai, oh rehn irail kan me malipilipda, (met uwen tohtohn irail akan me e ketin malipehda, oh ketikihong irail manaman oh mweimwei en papidais, iei meh ehkriemen) oh kilang, e ketin kapahwei limehu ong pokokon, oh mahsanihong irail, ketihtihki: Meid pai kumwail ma kumwail pahn rong mahsen kan en ehkriemenet, me I piladahr sang nanpwungamwail pwe re en papah kumwail, oh re en wia noumwail ladu; oh I kihong irail manaman en papidaisihkin kumwail pihl; oh mwurin amwail pahn papidaiskihla pihl, kilang, I pahn papidaisihkin kumwail kisiniei oh iangahki Ngehn Sarawi; eri meid pai kumwail ma kumwail pahn kamehlele ie oh papidaisla, mwurin amwail kilangiehier oh ese me iei Ngehi me.

2 Oh pil, meid pai mehlel irail me pahn kamehlele amwail koasoi kan pwehki amwail pahn kadehdehki me kumwail kilang ie, oh me kumwail ese me Ngehi me. Ei, meid pai irail me pahn kamehlele amwail koasoi kan, oh kohdo nan karakarahk oh papidaisla, pwe irail pahn alehdi kisiniei oh iangahki Ngehn Sarawi, oh pahn alehdi kamwakelpen diparail kan.

3 Ei, meid pai me aktikitik ni palingehn oh kohdo rehi, pwe iei arail wehin nanleng.

4 Oh pil, meid pai irail koaros me kin mwahiei, pwe [Kauno] pahn ketin kaloalamwawihirialla.

5 Oh meid pai me nan kapehd ohpampap, pwe irail pahn sohsohki sampah.

6 Oh meid pai irail koaros me kin men tungoale oh nim mour pwung, pwe irail pahn direkihla Ngehn Sarawi.

7 Oh meid pai me kin kalahngan ong meteikan, pwe irail pahn alehdi kalahngan.

8 Oh meid pai koaros me nan kapehd mwakelekel, pwe irail pahn udiahl Koht.

9 Oh meid pai koaros me kin wia doadoahk en kamwahu nanpwungen meteikan, pwe irail pahn kin likuwerki seri en Koht.

10 Oh meid pai irail koaros me kin lokolok pwehki mwarei, pwe iei arail wehin nanleng.

11 Oh meid pai kumwail ma aramas akan pahn lahlahwei kumwial oh kalokei kumwail, karaunkin kumwail soangen suwed oh likamw koaros, pwehki ngehi;

12 Pwe kumwail pahn nsenamwahu oh perenda mehlel, pwe ketingpamwail me laud nanleng; pwe ih duwen ar kaloke soukohp ako me tiengehr mwohmwail.

13 Mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, I kihong kumwail en wia soahlepen sampah; eri ma nemenemen soahl pahn sarasang, a ia mwomwen sampah eh pahn soahl? Soahlo pahn solahr katepe, ahpw e pahn lekdekla oh aramas akan pahn tiahkpeseng.

14 Mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, I kihong kumwail en wia marain en aramas pwukat. Kahnihmw ehu me mih pohn dohl ehu sohte kak rirla.

15 Kilang, aramas kin isikada lamp oh kihdiong pahn kohpwa? Soh, ahpw pohn dewe pwe en kamarainihada koaros me mi nan ihmwo;

16 Eri kumwail mweidehng amwail marain en sansal mwohn aramas pwukat, pwe irail en kak kilang amwail doadoahk mwahu kan oh kapikapingahki Samamwail me ketiket nanleng.

17 Kumwail dehr lemeleme me I kodohng kasohrehla kosonned en Moses de padahk en soukohp ako. I sohte kodohng kasohrehla, ahpw en kapwaiada;

18 Pwe mehlel I ndaiong kumwail, sohte ire pisetik ehu en kosonnedo pahn sohrala, ahpw sang rehi koaros pahn pweida.

19 Oh kilang, I kihong kumwail kosonnedo oh kosonned kan en Sahmo, kahrehda kumwail pahn kamehlele ie, oh kumwail pahn koluhkihla dipamwail kan, oh kohdo rehi nan mohngiong karakarahk oh ngehn peik. Kilang, kosonned kan mihmi mwohmwail, oh kosonndo pweidahr.

20 Eri kumwail kohdo rehi oh kumwail komourla; pwe mehlel I ndaiong kumwail, ma kumwail sohte pahn kapwaiada ei kosonned kan, me I kihong kumwail ahnsou wet, kumwail sohte pahn kak pidelong nan wehin nanleng.

21 Kumwail rongehr mehn mahs ako ar kin koasoia, oh e pil ntingdier mwohmwail, me kumwail sohte pahn kemehla aramas, oh mehmen me pahn kemehla aramas e pahn ale kadeikpe ni mwoalen kopwung en Koht;

22 Ahpw I ndaiong kumwail, me mehmen me pahn lingeringer pahn kompoakepah men pahn ale kadeikpe nan eh kopwungo. Oh mehmen me pahn ndaiong kompoakepah eh mwalaun suwed, e pahn ale kadeikpe nan kaunselo; oh mehmen me pahn ndaiong eh pweipwei, pahn ale kadeikpe nan kisiniei en ehl.

23 Eri, ma kumwail pahn kohdo rehi, de pahn inangih kohdo rehi, oh tamanda me kempoakepahmw men nsensuwed pahmw—

24 Kohwei mahs rehn kempoakepahmwo, oh kapwungala mahs nan pwungamwa, oh mwuri ke ahpw pahn pwurodo rehi nan mohngiong unsek mehlel, oh I pahn aleiukada.

25 Kapwungala mwadang nanpwung kowe oh imwintihtio ahnsou me ke mihmihte mwowe, pwe ede pahn poweiukidi, oh kowe lekdeklong an imweteng.

26 Mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, kumwail sohte pahn kapidohisang lao kumwail pwainla uwen sihnain koaros. Oh ahnsou me kumwail pahn mihmi nan imweteng, kumwail kak pwain ehute sihna? Mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, Soh.

27 Kilang, e ntingdier sang irail mehn mahs ako, me kumwail sohte pahn kamwahl;

28 Ahpw I ndaiong kumwail, mehmen me pahn kilikilang lih emen oh men dihpki, e wiadahr kamwahl nan mohngiongi.

29 Kilang, I kihong kumwail kosonned ehu, me kumwail en dehr mweidehng mepwukat en pidelong nan mohngiongamwail;

30 Pwe e pahn mwahu me kumwail soikasang kumwail mepwukat, ni amwail pahn wia kumwail pahn alehda amwail lohpwu, e pahn mwahusang ma kumwail pahn lekdekla nan ehl.

31 E ntingdier, me mehmen me pahn kesehla eh pwoud, e pahn kihong liho kisinlikoun kamweid.

32 Mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, me mehmen me pahn mweisang eh pwoud ni kahrepe ieu me kaidehkin kamwahl, kahrehiongehr liho nan kamwahl; oh mehmen me pahn pwoudikihda liho me mweisangehr eh pwoudo, pil wiadahr dipen kamwahl.

33 Oh e pil ntingdier, kumwail dehr wiahda inou mwahl, ahpw kapwaiad dahme ke kahukihla me ke pahn wiahiong Kauno;

34 Ahpw mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, kumwail dehr mwahn kahula; de pil kaukihla nanleng, pwe nanleng iei mwoalen Koht;

35 De pil kahukihla sampah, pwe sampah iei wasahn kommoalepen aluweluwe kan;

36 Kumwail sohte pahn pil kahukihla moangemwail kan, pwe sohte mehkot kumwail kak wiahda pwe pitenmoangamwail en pwetepwetala de toantoalla;

37 Ahpw amwail koasoi kan en kin, Ei, ei; Soh, soh; pwe me kin daulihala met e suwed.

38 Oh kilang, e ntingdier, pwoaren mas ehu pahn pwainla pwoaren mas ehu, oh ngih pwoat pil pahn pwainla ngih pwoat;

39 Ahpw I ndaiong kumwail, me kumwail sohte pahn dupungki me suwed ong emen me wia suwed ong kumwail, ahpw mehmen me pahn pohr uhk ni palimaun en likin sepomw, a ke en pil kihong pali teio;

40 Oh ma aramas men pahn lelekin uhk ni mwoalen kowpung pwe en adihasang omw sehten, a pil mweidohng omw sekiden;

41 Oh ma mehmen pahn itonehng uhk ke en iangala mwail ehu, a ke iangala mwail riau.

42 Kihong me pahn peki rehm mehkot, oh mehmen me pahn peki rehmw mehkot pwe en kapwuredohng uhk mwuhr dehr sohpeisang.

43 Oh kilang e pil ntingdier, kumwail pahn poako; hng mehn mpomw oh kailongki omw imwintihti kan;

44 Ahpw kilang I ndaiong kumwail, poakehng amwail imwintihti kan, kapaia irail me kin keriah kumwail, oh wia mwahu ong irail me kin kailongkin kumwail, oh kapakpaki irail me kin wiakauwe oh kaloke kumwail;

45 Pwe kumwail en wia sapwellimen Sahm me ketiket nanleng; me kin ketin dakerki sapwellime ketipin pohn me suwed oh me mwahu kan.

46 Eri soahng kan me mehn mahs ako, me mih pahn kosonnedo, koaros pweidahr rehi.

47 Soahng kan me mehn mahs imwiseklahr, oh soahng koaros weliakapwalahr.

48 Eri I men mourimwail en unsek duwehte ngehi, de Samamwailo me ketiket nanleng me unsek.

3-ne 21:
[center][font_size=26]Iralaud 21[/font_size][/center]

[i]Israel pahn kopwurupwurpene ahnsou me Pwuhk en Mormon pahn kohdo—Mehn Liki kan pahn wiahla aramas saledek nan Amerika—Irail pahn komourla ma irail pahn kamehlele oh peik; ma soh, irail pahn lekidekla oh kamwomwala—Israel pahn kauada Serusalem Kapw, oh keinek me salongala ko pahn pwurehng pwurodo. Ele Sounpar 34 Mwurin Ipwidi en Krais.[/i]

1 Oh mehlel I ndaiong kumwail, I kihong kumwail ehu kilel, pwe kumwail en kak ese ahnsou me mepwukat pahn tepida wiawi—me I pahn kapwurehdo nei aramas akan, peneinei en Israel, sang wasa irail salongala ie ahnsou werei, oh pahn pwurehng wiahda Saion rehrail;

2 Oh kilang, iei met me I pahn kihong kumwail pwe en wia kilel ehu—pwe kilang I ndaiong kumwail me ahnsou me mepwukat me I ndaiong kumwail, oh me I pahn pein ndaiong kumwail mwurin met, oh sang ni manaman en Ngehn Sarawi me pahn kohieng kumwail sang rehn Sahmo, pahn sansalohng Mehn Liki kan pwe irail en esehda duwen aramas pwukat me wia kisehn peneinei en Seikop, oh duwen nei aramas pwukat me irail pahn pwakihpeseng;

3 Mehlel, mehlel, I ndaiong kumwail, ahnsou me Sahmo pahn ketin kasalehiong irail mepwukat, oh Sahmo ketikihong kumwail sang rehrail;

4 Pwe iei sapwellimen Sahmo eripit, irail en kousoanla pohn sahpwet, oh wiahla aramas saledek kei sang ni manaman en Sahmo, pwe mepwukat en kak kohdohng kisehn kadaudokemwail akan sang rehrail, pwe inou en Sahmo en kak pweida me e ketin inoukihong sapwellime aramas, peneinei en Israel;

5 Eri, ahnsou me doadoahk pwukat oh doadoahk kan me pahn kohieng kumwail mwurin met pahn kohsang Mehn Liki kan, oh kohdohng kadaudokemwail akan me pahn pwupwikihdi sohpwoson pwehki wiewia suwed;

6 Pwe kilang met iei kupwur en Sahmo me e pahn kohsang rehn Mehn Liki kan, pwe en ketin kasalehiong sapwellime manaman ong Mehn Liki kan, pwe kahrepe wet me Mehn Liki kan, ma irail sohte pahn keptakaiala mohngiongarail kan, pwe irail en kak koluhla oh kohdo rehi oh papidaisla ni mwarei oh esehla iren ei padahk pwung kan, pwe irail en iang wadawadiong rehn nei aramas akan, peneinei en Israel;

7 Oh ahnsou mepwukat pahn pweida me kadaudokemwail kan pahn tepida wehwehkihda mepwukat—e pahn wia kilel ehu ong irail, pwe irail pahn ese me sapwellimen Sahmo doadoahk tepidahr ong pweidahn inouo me e ketin inoukihong aramas akan me wia peneinei en Israel.

8 Oh ahnsou me rahn pahn leledo, e pahn pweida me nanmwarki kan pahn pwuriamwei, re sohla pahn kak mahsen, pwe re pahn mahsanihada oh mwahngihadamehkot me re sohte kin karonge oh mwahngih sang mahs kohdo.

9 Pwe ni rahno, Semeio pahn ketin wia doadoahk ehu pwehki ngehi, me pahn wia doadoahk kesempwal oh kapwuriamwei rehn aramas akan; oh e pahn mie rehrail irail akan me sohte kin kamehlele, ahpw aramas pahn kin kalohngkihong irail.

10 Ahpw kilang, mour en ei laduo pahn mihmi nan pehi; eri irail sohte pahn kamedekehla, ahpw e pahn wekila pwehki irail. Ahpw I pahn kamwahuiala, pwe I pahn kasalehiong irail me ei eripit lapasang widing en tepilo.

11 Eri ahnsouo pahn leledo me mehmen me sohte pahn kamehlele ei mahsen kan, ngehi iei Sises Krais, me Sahmo pahn ketin wiahiong ih en wahdohng Mehn Liki kan, oh pahn kihong ih manaman pwe en kak wahdohng Mehn Liki kan, (e pahn pweida nin duwen Moses e mahsanih) irail pahn lekidekla sang rehn nei aramas akan me wia aramas en inouo.

12 Oh nei aramas akan me wia kisehn kadaudok en Seikop pahn mih rehn Mehn Liki kan, ei, nanpwungarail duwehte laion men nan pwungen mahn en nanwel kan, oh duwehte laion pwulopwul men nan pwungen pelin sihpw, me, ma e pahn kohwei e pahn tiakiraildi oh tehrirailpeseng, oh sohte me kak doarehla.

13 Pehrail kan pahn kohdahng pohn amwail imwintihti kan, oh amwail imwintihti koaros pahn kamala.

14 Ei, meid suwediong Mehn Liki kan ihte ma irail koluhla; pwe rahno pahn leledo, Sahmo ketin mahsanih, me I pahn kemehla weremwail oahs akan sang rehmwail, oh I pahn kawehla weremwail werennansapw kan;

15 Oh I pahn kawehla amwail kahnihmw kan, oh kesehdi kehl kehlail kan;

16 Oh I pahn kemehla sounwunahni kan sang nan sapwamwail kan, oh sohla pahn mie amwail sounkosetipw;

17 I pahn kawehla amwail dikedik en eni kan, oh I pahn kawehla amwail dikedik en eni me uhda kan, oh kumwail sohla pahn pwongih doadoahk en pehmwail kan;

18 Oh I pahn usadahsang amwail tuhkehkan mwohmwail; duwehte ei pahn kawehla amwail kahnihmw kan.

19 Oh ahnsouo pahn leledo me likamw kan, oh ketewehdi kan, oh noahrok kan, oh akamai kan, oh prihskrap kan, oh kamwahl akan koaros, pahn imwisekla.

20 Pwe ahnsouo pahn leledo, Sahmo mahsanih, me ni rahno mehmen me sohte pahn koluhla oh kohdo rehn nei Pwukat Kempoakeo, I pahn kalipasang irail rehn nei aramas akan, peneinei en Israel;

21 Oh ni ei engieng laud I pahn dupukiong irail, duwehte me rotorot akan, pwehki arail sohte kin rong ie.

22 Ahpw ma irail pahn koluhla oh rong ei mahsen kan, oh sohte keptakaiala mohngiongarail kan, I pahn wiahda ei mwomwohdiso rehrail, oh irail pahn pidelong nan inouo oh iang wadawadiong rehn kisehn kadaudok en Seikop, me I kihongehr sahpwet en wia arail sohso;

23 Oh irail pahn sowese nei aramas akan, kisehn kadaudok en Seikop, oh pil koaros peneinei en Israel me pahn kohdo, pwe irail en kauada kahnihmw ehu, me pahn kahdanihki Serusalem Kapw.

24 Oh irail pahn sowese kapwurehdo nei aramas akan nan Serusalem Kapw, aramas akan me mwerpesengehr pohn sahpwe pwon.

25 Oh manaman en nanleng ahpw pahn kohieng irail; oh I pahn pil ieiang irail.

26 Oh sapwellimen Sahmo doadoahk ahpw pahn tepida nan ahnsouo, iei ahsouo rongamwahu wet pahn kalohkohng kisehn aramas pwukat. Mehlel I ndaiong kumwail, ni ahnsouo sapwellimen Sahmo doadoahk pahn tepida rehn nei aramas koaros me salongpeseng, iei, keinek kan me salongalahr, me Sahmo ketin kahluwahsang nan Serusalem.

27 Ei, doadoahk wet pahn tepida rehn nei aramas koaros me salongpeseng, oh Sahmo pahn ketin kaunopada ahlo pwe irail en kak pwurodo rehi, pwe irail en kak eker Sahmo ni mwarei.

28 Ei, oh doadoahk wet ahpw pahn tepida, oh Sahmo pahn ketin kaunopada wehi koaros pwe sapwellime aramas akan en kak kopwurupwurdohng imwarail nan sapwarail sahpw en sohso.

29 Oh irail pahn kohwei sang nan wehi koaros; oh irail sohte pahn kohwei ni karuaru de sopohla; pwe I pahn tihengwei mwohmwail, Sahmo ketin mahsanih, oh I pahn sinsile mwurumwail.
